title: A.D. Machico (volleyball)
text:
Associação Desportiva de Machico has a <a href="Volleyball">Volleyball</a> team based in <a href="Machico">Machico</a>, <a href="Madeira">Madeira</a>, <a href="Portugal">Portugal</a>. It plays in <a href="Portuguese%20Volleyball%20League%20A1">Portuguese Volleyball League A1</a>. It is part of its parent club <a href="A.D.%20Machico">A.D. Machico</a>, which also runs a semi-professional <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> team.
Achievements.
2005/06
